{"tid":2020834,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"喺街度見到班走狗，請用詛咒嘅眼神望住佢哋","createTime":"2020-05-17T11:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T11:13:23.000Z","uid":125434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a82bd8526037e45bfe5215872689ec1d6a7042a1","tid":2020834,"uid":125434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T11:03:26.000Z","msg":"每次喺街度見到有走狗，大部份人都會避開同佢地有眼神接觸，其實係啱啱相反。<br />\n<br />\n我哋係要每個人都用充滿仇恨同埋詛咒嘅眼神望住佢哋，要比心理壓力佢哋，要佢哋真痴線，要佢哋發夢都見到你<br />\n痛狠嘅眼神，要佢哋知道自己係一班維護極權嘅地獄走狗，全香港人都好想佢哋落地獄。<br />\n<br />\n請由今天開始，認真地從日常生活出發，好好鄙視佢哋。<br />\n<br />\n已經係唔需要你講任何野撚狗，亦都唔需要你出手。<br />\n<br />\n你嘅任何一個方法同埋行動都有可能成為導火線推倒呢個政權，唔怕做多，只怕你連少少野都唔肯做。"},{"pid":"c3b1547f63364c37f0ec257c90ed61ae8d053d7e","tid":2020834,"uid":142987,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T11:08:07.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e45105885e7572b53862f23f83ed3e5ae3f899ef","tid":2020834,"uid":265192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T11:13:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尚欠91%！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EQt3hkf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEQt3hkf.jpg&h=d8fea6e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌連結</span>：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3cMLSEJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3cMLSEJ&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e61%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=0effde46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3cMLSEJ</a></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n來源（區議員認證）：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/915080692167681/posts/1162995320709549/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F915080692167681%2Fposts%2F1162995320709549%2F&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e61%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=6b40798e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com